            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>福泰製藥(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:VRTX:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/VRTX\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">VRTX-US</a>)截至台北時間03日22:45股價上漲21.85美元，報455.00美元，漲幅5.04%，成交量287,450（股），盤中最高價455.01美元、最低價439.35美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.03%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.16%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.4%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-0.37%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>福泰製藥(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:VRTX:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/VRTX\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">VRTX-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-0.98%</li> <li>近 1 月：-0.09%</li> <li>近 3 月：+6.13%</li> <li>近 6 月：-4.45%</li> <li>今年以來：+4.89%</li></ul></section></main>",
